Just that he has a
bland appetite.

26
00:04:12,250 --> 00:04:15,458
He ate some bread, drank
some water and went to bed.

27
00:04:15,916 --> 00:04:19,041
His existence really does
revolve around his work, huh?

28
00:04:19,125 --> 00:04:22,125
I'm guessing he's lived
his whole life this way.

29
00:04:24,083 --> 00:04:28,041
They're not human.
They're basically objects.

30
00:04:29,166 --> 00:04:30,250
Thirsty?

31
00:04:33,708 --> 00:04:37,291
Thanks so much, Hitomi.
But you really didn't have to

