00:04:37,375 --> 00:04:40,250
go to the trouble of
bringing me extra clothes.

33
00:04:40,833 --> 00:04:42,833
You should be with your baby.

34
00:04:42,916 --> 00:04:45,500
Oh it's fine, Yoshitsune
offered to babysit.

35
00:04:45,583 --> 00:04:48,000
Besides, it's nice to have
a little break from the

36
00:04:48,083 --> 00:04:51,958
baby every once in a while.
This is like a short vacation.

37
00:04:52,958 --> 00:04:55,833
It doesn't even matter if
they lose their families.

38
00:04:55,916 --> 00:04:58,666
They can simply
collect a replacement.

39
00:04:59,875 --> 00:05:03,875
It's so weird how delicate our
society is. Gaia carefully

